A_4 = #{(s1,s2,s3,s4) Ôłł QRÔü┤ : all partial sums distinct}

Automatic conditions (from -1 Ôłë QR for p Ôëí 3 mod 4):
  s1 Ôëá 0, s1+s2 Ôëá 0, s2 Ôëá 0, s3 Ôëá 0, s4 Ôëá 0, s3+s4 Ôëá 0

Non-automatic conditions:
  (i)   s1+s2+s3 Ôëá 0
  (ii)  s1+s2+s3+s4 Ôëá 0
  (iii) s2+s3+s4 Ôëá 0

By PIE: A_4 = mÔü┤ - |S_i Ôł¬ S_ii Ôł¬ S_iii| where S_x = violations of condition x.


